      ‚úì applies multiple filters simultaneously (129 ms)
      ‚úì resets all filters (147 ms)

      ‚úì applies custom className (30 ms)
      ‚úì applies custom style (32 ms)

      ‚úì does not render grid lines when showGrid is false (8 ms)
      ‚úì uses chartTimeData for grid alignment when provided (22 ms)

      ‚úì does not render today marker when showToday is false (26 ms)

      ‚úì renders different dependency types with different colors (31 ms)

      ‚úì calls onBrushChange when dragging in brush mode (44 ms)
      ‚úì displays brush overlay when brushRange is provided (26 ms)

      ‚úì calls onItemMove when dragging an item (62 ms)
      ‚úì calls onItemEdit when double-clicking an item (28 ms)
      ‚úì calls onItemDelete when right-clicking an item (44 ms)
      ‚úì calls onItemAdd when double-clicking empty space (36 ms)
    Tooltips
      ‚úì shows tooltip on hover in phase-manager mode (41 ms)
      ‚úì hides tooltip on mouse leave (58 ms)
      ‚úì updates tooltip position on mouse move (61 ms)
    Phase Handles
      ‚úì renders phase handles in phase-manager mode (28 ms)
      ‚úì does not render phase handles in brush mode (33 ms)
      ‚úì calls onItemResize when clicking extend handle (27 ms)
    Resize Handles
      ‚úì renders resize handles on item hover in phase-manager mode (45 ms)
      ‚úì calls onItemResize when dragging resize handle (94 ms)
    Keyboard Shortcuts
      ‚úì triggers phase action on Enter key when handle is hovered (29 ms)
    Empty States
      ‚úì renders empty timeline with no items (32 ms)
      ‚úì renders timeline with no dependencies (25 ms)
    Edge Cases
      ‚úì handles items with minimum width (37 ms)
      ‚úì handles items outside viewport (20 ms)
      ‚úì handles overlapping items (34 ms)
      ‚úì enforces minimum item duration when resizing (65 ms)
